skdetail:

Invocation Name: main site
des: This Alexa skill can be used to check the www.crossfit.com workout which gets posted for the public every day. In no way does this skill take credit for writing the workout, it merely delivers it to you following a simple request. Never leave the house without first knowing what main site has in store for you!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
